01:12:07.100 --> 01:12:12.300
I don't know my music history so well, but equal temperament is a way of sort of pushing

01:12:12.300 --> 01:12:17.420
this clean mathematical representation of pitch into something that is more regular and that

01:12:17.420 --> 01:12:20.740
can be, for instance, transposed and…

01:12:20.740 --> 01:12:21.740
Exactly.

01:12:21.740 --> 01:12:24.300
