01:16:38.740 --> 01:16:46.220
masters at, where you find it maybe almost breaking apart to this space where you're

01:16:46.220 --> 01:16:50.780
not even sure if it's music anymore, where you're right on that boundary.

01:16:50.780 --> 01:16:58.220
