01:18:04.580 --> 01:18:06.460
I mean, we're all improvisers.

01:18:06.460 --> 01:18:11.580
I mean, in the same way that we can debate until the cows come home if they ever do.

01:18:11.580 --> 01:18:13.460
I don't know if people stay there anymore.

01:18:13.460 --> 01:18:19.420
