01:18:19.420 --> 01:18:25.020
And the more you examine that concept, it also kind of melts away in the sense that, well,

01:18:25.020 --> 01:18:28.860
everything we do is improvised, except the things that aren't.

01:18:28.860 --> 01:18:34.100
And that stuff we know, like, well, oh, they all did the same thing at the same time, so

01:18:34.100 --> 01:18:35.860
they probably weren't improvising.

01:18:35.860 --> 01:18:38.020
Like they must have…how do they know how to do that?

01:18:38.020 --> 01:18:43.340
